  steps:
  - text: "Une fois envoy\xE9s, les documents sont trait\xE9s par les p\xF4les correspondants."
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 1
    unpauseOnClose: 0
    overrideButtonSprite: 0
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a6a64769997ed734985232f808762c0b, type: 3}
    pressedButtonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c5c1ea00977a06a47895f9f5850af686, type: 3}
    overrideButtonSize: 0
    buttonSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overrideButtonPosition: 0
    buttonPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    showBackButton: 0
    overridePanelSize: 0
    panelSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overridePanelPosition: 0
    panelPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - text: "Sur votre ordinateur, vous pouvez suivre leur progression et voir quels
      employ\xE9s travaillent et ne travaillent pas."
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 1
    unpauseOnClose: 0
    overrideButtonSprite: 0
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a6a64769997ed734985232f808762c0b, type: 3}
    pressedButtonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c5c1ea00977a06a47895f9f5850af686, type: 3}
    overrideButtonSize: 0
    buttonSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overrideButtonPosition: 0
    buttonPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    showBackButton: 0
    overridePanelSize: 0
    panelSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overridePanelPosition: 0
    panelPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - text: " Chaque employ\xE9 vous rapporte ainsi une certaine somme en fonction
      de sa productivit\xE9."
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 0
    unpauseOnClose: 0
    overrideButtonSprite: 0
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: adcee05d20d5e0b40b6c64ed512eb934, type: 3}
    pressedButtonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d06654f2adf418e4192ccf8c2d3d6ec8, type: 3}
    overrideButtonSize: 0
    buttonSize: {x: 300, y: 300}
    overrideButtonPosition: 0
    buttonPosition: {x: -100, y: 0}
    showBackButton: 1
    overridePanelSize: 0
    panelSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overridePanelPosition: 0
    panelPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - text: "Les post-its sous l'\xE9cran montrent que des papiers ont \xE9t\xE9 envoy\xE9s
      dans les p\xF4les. "
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 0
    unpauseOnClose: 0
    overrideButtonSprite: 0
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: adcee05d20d5e0b40b6c64ed512eb934, type: 3}
    pressedButtonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d06654f2adf418e4192ccf8c2d3d6ec8, type: 3}
    overrideButtonSize: 0
    buttonSize: {x: 300, y: 300}
    overrideButtonPosition: 0
    buttonPosition: {x: -100, y: 0}
    showBackButton: 1
    overridePanelSize: 0
    panelSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overridePanelPosition: 0
    panelPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - text: "La barre montre la dur\xE9e de vie du papier dans le p\xF4le avant qu'il
      ne se d\xE9truise, s'il n'est pas trait\xE9 par un employ\xE9. "
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 0
    unpauseOnClose: 0
    overrideButtonSprite: 0
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: adcee05d20d5e0b40b6c64ed512eb934, type: 3}
    pressedButtonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d06654f2adf418e4192ccf8c2d3d6ec8, type: 3}
    overrideButtonSize: 0
    buttonSize: {x: 300, y: 300}
    overrideButtonPosition: 0
    buttonPosition: {x: -100, y: 0}
    showBackButton: 1
    overridePanelSize: 0
    panelSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    overridePanelPosition: 0
    panelPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  - text: "Quand l\u2019ic\xF4ne d'un personnage est dessus, cela signifie qu'un
      employ\xE9 est actuellement sur la t\xE2che. "
    stepType: 0
    pauseOnShow: 0
    unpauseOnClose: 1
    overrideButtonSprite: 1
    buttonSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: adcee05d20d5e0b40b6c64ed512eb934, type: 3}
